OL,4,CEx-prosecutor Nazir Afzal to lead
OL,5,CCatholic Church child abuse body
OL,6, The former chief crown prosecutor in
OL,7, the Rochdale grooming gang cases has
OL,8, been appointed as the chairman of the
OL,9, Catholic Church's new safeguarding body
OL,10, in England and Wales.
OL,12,FNazir Afzal's appointment was welcomed
OL,13,Fby two survivors of abuse, who said "a
OL,14,Fseismic shift in culture" was needed.
OL,16,FThe body will be able to sanction
OL,17,Fclergy who do not meet standards.
OL,19,FIt comes after the Church was heavily
OL,20,Fcriticised for its response to child
OL,21,Fabuse by an independent inquiry.
